  "analyst_note": "CVE-2013-4316: Apache Struts 2.0.0-2.3.15.2 ExceptionDelegator RCE via OGNL expression in exception messages. Struts version is not typically exposed in HTTP headers \u2014 detection relies on .action or .do URL patterns (indicators of Struts). If Struts is suspected, check for X-Struts-Version header or error page contents. Fixed: 2.3.15.3.",
